# GOLDEN Rlow Rhigh DISJOINT
# GROUND-TRUTH: g is the same filtered jet collection in both regions; Rlow needs size(g)<=1, Rhigh needs size(g)>=2. A single integer count cannot be both <=1 and >=2. Event {1 jet pt=40} in Rlow only; {2 jets pt>=35} in Rhigh only; {} in Rlow only.
# Opposite size cuts on the SAME object make the regions disjoint.

object g
  take Jet
  select pt > 30

region Rlow
  select size(g) <= 1

region Rhigh
  select size(g) >= 2
